[h3]Hearts of Iron IV's 9th Anniversary![/h3]
As apart of HOI IV's [i][b]Ninth[/b][/i] anniversary, we've decided to do another giveaway with a different prize each day including some fan favourites and some keys for the new Song pack for those of you who missed out on some of those banger tunes. To participate and enter for a chance to win some of these codes, make sure to reply in the announcement post on each day you want to take part in the giveaway.

Because of time zones, we've decided that each giveaway "day" will start at [b]14:00 CEST[/b], so for example, if you want to take part in the Bonus Songs Pack giveaway on Tuesday, then you need to reply between [b]14:00 CEST[/b] on Tuesday and [b]13:59 CEST[/b] on Wednesday. If you reply on Wednesday [b]14:00 CEST[/b], then you're taking part in the Wednesday giveaway, etc.

You can reply as many times as you want, on as many days as you want, but if we're looking through replies and have to choose between two replies, we will probably choose the reply that has some substance (vs "Just replying to take part") so be creative, engage, comment on the announcement or on others' replies.

[list]
[*] Today: [url=https://store.steampowered.com/sub/1044814/]HOI IV Starter Edition[/url] [i]So you can play with more friends[/i] x30
[*] Tomorrow:[url=https://store.steampowered.com/app/3654400/Hearts_of_Iron_IV_Bonus_Songs_Pack/]Bonus Songs Pack[/url] [i]To listen to, even when you're paused[/i] x30
[*] Wednesday:[url=https://store.steampowered.com/app/1348661/Expansion__Hearts_of_Iron_IV_No_Step_Back/]No Step Back[/url] [i]To bring Communism to the World[/i] x30
[*] Thursday:[url=https://store.steampowered.com/app/1880650/Expansion__Hearts_of_Iron_IV_By_Blood_Alone/]By Blood Alone[/url] [i]Take your fight to the Skies[/i] x30
[*] Friday:[url=https://store.steampowered.com/app/2183930/Expansion__Hearts_of_Iron_IV_Arms_Against_Tyranny/]Arms Against Tyranny[/url] [i]To bring the fight to the Nordics[/i] x30
[/list]

